{"comments":"AnimationPhase — Bounded normalized animation time (0.0-1.0).\n\nRepresents the progress through an animation curve:\n- **0.0**: Animation start\n- **0.5**: Animation midpoint\n- **1.0**: Animation complete\n\nThis is the fundamental atom for animation state. Combined with easing\nfunctions, it drives all temporal interpolation in the rendering pipeline.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nThe phase is always normalized [0.0, 1.0] regardless of actual duration.\nThis decouples animation logic from wall-clock time, enabling:\n- Deterministic replay at any speed\n- Reversible animations (phase can decrease)\n- Loop detection (phase wraps at 1.0)\n- Scrubbing (set phase directly for preview)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[68,54],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[68,1]},"title":"eqAnimationPhase"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[69,56],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[69,1]},"title":"ordAnimationPhase"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[72,54],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[71,1]},"title":"showAnimationPhase"}],"comments":"Normalized animation phase (0.0-1.0)\n\nRepresents progress through an animation. 0.0 is the start, 1.0 is complete.\nBounded by construction — invalid phases cannot exist.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[66,47],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[66,1]},"title":"AnimationPhase"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create an AnimationPhase, clamping to valid range [0.0, 1.0]\n\nValues outside the range are clamped:\n```purescript\nanimationPhase 0.5   -- AnimationPhase 0.5\nanimationPhase 1.5   -- AnimationPhase 1.0 (clamped)\nanimationPhase (-0.2) -- AnimationPhase 0.0 (clamped)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[86,43],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[86,1]},"title":"animationPhase"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create an AnimationPhase without clamping\n\nUse only when you know the value is valid [0.0, 1.0].\nInvalid values will break invariants.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[93,49],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[93,1]},"title":"unsafeAnimationPhase"},{"children":[],"comments":"Extract the raw Number value [0.0, 1.0]\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[201,35],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[201,1]},"title":"unwrap"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert to Number (alias for unwrap)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[205,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[205,1]},"title":"toNumber"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create phase from Number (alias for animationPhase)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[97,39],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[97,1]},"title":"fromNumber"},{"children":[],"comments":"Advance the phase by a delta, clamping to [0.0, 1.0]\n\nFor forward-playing animations:\n```purescript\nadvance 0.1 (animationPhase 0.5)  -- AnimationPhase 0.6\nadvance 0.3 (animationPhase 0.9)  -- AnimationPhase 1.0 (clamped)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[111,54],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[111,1]},"title":"advance"},{"children":[],"comments":"Reverse the phase by a delta (move backward), clamping to [0.0, 1.0]\n\nFor reverse-playing animations:\n```purescript\nreverse 0.1 (animationPhase 0.5)  -- AnimationPhase 0.4\nreverse 0.3 (animationPhase 0.1)  -- AnimationPhase 0.0 (clamped)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[121,54],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[121,1]},"title":"reverse"},{"children":[],"comments":"Wrap the phase at boundaries (for looping animations)\n\nWhen phase exceeds 1.0, wrap to 0.0 and continue:\n```purescript\nwrap (animationPhase 0.5)  -- AnimationPhase 0.5\nwrap (animationPhase 1.2)  -- AnimationPhase 0.2 (wrapped)\nwrap (animationPhase 2.5)  -- AnimationPhase 0.5 (wrapped)\nwrap (animationPhase (-0.3))  -- AnimationPhase 0.7 (wrapped)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[133,41],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[133,1]},"title":"wrap"},{"children":[],"comments":"Clamp the phase to [0.0, 1.0] (explicit clamp operation)\n\nUseful when composing with operations that might exceed bounds:\n```purescript\nclamp (unsafeAnimationPhase 1.5)  -- AnimationPhase 1.0\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[155,42],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[155,1]},"title":"clamp"},{"children":[],"comments":"Check if animation is complete (phase >= 1.0)\n\nUseful for cleanup and state transitions:\n```purescript\nisComplete (animationPhase 1.0)   -- true\nisComplete (animationPhase 0.99)  -- false\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[183,40],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[183,1]},"title":"isComplete"},{"children":[],"comments":"Check if animation has started (phase > 0.0)\n\nUseful for detecting animation activation:\n```purescript\nisStarted (animationPhase 0.0)    -- false\nisStarted (animationPhase 0.01)   -- true\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","AnimationPhase"],"AnimationPhase"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[193,39],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/AnimationPhase.purs","start":[193,1]},"title":"isStarted"},{"children":[],"comments":"Blend two animation phases with weight\n\nLinear interpolation between phases:\n```purescript\nblend 0.0 (animationPhase 0.2) (animationPhase 0.8)  -- AnimationPhase 0.2\nblend 0.5 (animationPhase 0.2) (animationPhase 0.8)  -- AnimationPhase 0.5\nblend 1.0 (animationPhase 0.2) (animationPhase 0.8)  -- AnimationPhase 0.8\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotati